    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>peanut butter</strong> in 250ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [350ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>,<strong> lime leaf[ves]</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your<strong> peanut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
