    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper and onion have softened, add your <strong>red</strong> <strong>Thai curry paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>peanut stock</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until the sauce has thickened</p>",
