    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has started to thicken, add your <strong>meat-free chick'n </strong>and cook for 5-9 min further or until warmed through</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your<strong> Southern Thai-style meat-free chick'n Panang curry</strong></p><p>Tip: If the curry is looking a little dry, add a splash of water to loosen the sauce</p><p>Fluff the<strong> basmati rice</strong> with a fork and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
