    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Southern Thai-style meat-free chick'n Panang curry </strong>with the <strong>basmati rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Discard the<strong> lime leaf[ves]</strong> and garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
